data.description: SELLER IS RELOCATING AND MOTIVATED TO SELL! This is an exciting opportunity to make this stunning home yours! Priced to sell! Assumable 3.99% loan! WELCOME HOME to this stunning ranch-style Inspirada home. Built by luxury builder Toll Brothers, the home showcases numerous upgrades throughout, PLUS the Owners invested $180,000 to create a backyard oasis that provides enjoyment year-round * Freshly painted interior * The home’s generous floor plan offers a well-appointed kitchen with high-end Thermador appliances and walk-in pantry. The great room features warm finishes and integrates the family room with dining areas. Four bedrooms provide ample living space, and the primary bedroom suite includes a luxurious bath and oversized walk-in custom closet. Exterior amenities include the beach entry Pebbletec pool, spa, three pergolas, firepit, synthetic turf, and multiple entertaining/play areas. Access to an array of amenities including parks, walking trails, small shops, and more.
